ns.” Vanguard News AN activist and former labour leader in Delta State, Comrade Ovuozourie Macaulay, Thursday urged the leadership of the National Assembly, NASS and Nigeria’s Governors Forum, NGF to come together and dialogue with the leadership of the #ENDSARS protesters with a view to finding an amicable solution to the demands of… October 22, 2020 In "News" WARRI- THE son of the Secretary to the State Government, SSG, Delta State, Comrade Ovuozourie Macaulay was kidnapped, Monday, at his home town, Owheologbo, near Ozoro, in Isoko North Local Government Area of the state. June 18, 2012 In "News" A former Secretary to Delta State Government, Comrade Ovuozourie Macaulay has described former Delta State Governor, Chief James Onanefe Ibori as a man whose unheeded forecast for a progressive Nigeria would have saved the country's polity from its coeval incessant strife. August 4, 2019 In "News"